OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPatches of low cloud and any
OL,6,Ffog will soon clear to leave a dry day
OL,7,Facross the region. There will be some
OL,8,Fdecent spells of sunshine, and with
OL,9,Flight winds it will feel very warm
OL,10,Fagain in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be a dry evening with
OL,13,Flong clear periods. Patches of cloud
OL,14,Fare likely to drift across from the
OL,15,Fnorth overnight, though it should stay
OL,16,Fdry. Quite warm too.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
