OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAnother largely fine day is
OL,6,Fexpected on Saturday with some warm
OL,7,Fsunshine developing. However, cloud
OL,8,Fwill increase from the northwest later
OL,9,Fon in the day, bringing some patchy
OL,10,Flight rain.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,13,Fwill be a fresher, still breezy day
OL,14,Fwith sunshine and a few light showers.
OL,15,FMostly dry early on next week, with
OL,16,Fsome sunny spells, especially in the
OL,17,Feast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
